[SN]TITLE[SN]
Stockwell Tube passenger hit by train

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
A man is believed to have been struck by a train at Stockwell Tube station.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
Eyewitnesses on Twitter described the accident as "horrific" and that the man was hit when he bent down to pick up his bag.
British Transport Police said the man had life-threatening head injuries and was in a critical condition.
